  ('commercial', 'Mayco', 'Jungle Gems', 'CG-997', 'Seafoam', 'Cone 06 / Cone 10 / Cone 6', 'Cone 06 oxidation (large photo): Seafoam is a translucent turquoise base glaze with a variety of white crystals that bloom. Cone 6 oxidation (small photo): Base glaze fades – crystals fade completely. Enhanced mobility. Surface issues may occur.'),
