  ('commercial', 'Mayco', 'E-Z Stroke Translucent Underglazes', 'EZ011', 'Sienna Brown', 'Cone 06 / Cone 10 / Cone 6', 'Cone 06 oxidation: Sienna Brown is a translucent underglaze suitable for use with a number of decorating techniques including airbrushing, antiquing and brushstrokes. Cone 6 oxidation: Minimal change in color. Recommended clear: SW001 Stoneware Clear. Cone 10 reduction: Minimal change in color. Recommended clear: SW001 Stoneware Clear.'),
