  ('commercial', 'Mayco', 'Cobblestone', 'SG-201', 'Black Cobblestone', 'Cone 06 / Cone 6', 'Cone 06 oxidation (large photo): A black shattered pattern of raised, irregular chips will emerge. The underlying glaze will appear in the cracks. Cone 6 oxidation (small photo): Glaze will bead up on the surface of the piece. If applied over another glaze the texture flattens with similar cobblestone pattern.'),
  ('commercial', 'Mayco', 'Cobblestone', 'SG-202', 'White Cobblestone', 'Cone 06 / Cone 6', 'Cone 06 oxidation (large photo): A white shattered pattern of raised, irregular chips will emerge. The underlying glaze will appear in the cracks. Cone 6 oxidation (small photo): Glaze will bead up on the surface of the piece. If applied over another glaze the texture flattens with similar cobblestone pattern.'),
  ('commercial', 'Mayco', 'Snowfall', 'SG-302', 'Snowfall', 'Cone 06 / Cone 10 / Cone 6', 'Cone 06 oxidation (large photo): Creates a white, textured surface. Cone 6 oxidation (small photo): No change.'),
