  ('commercial', 'Mayco', 'Designer Liner', 'SG-405', 'Green', 'Cone 06 / Cone 10 / Cone 6', 'Cone 06 oxidation (large photo): Use this versatile product to create green fine detail with lines, dots, and letters. Cone 6 oxidation (small photo): No color change. TIP: If applying a clear glaze, use SW-004 Zinc Free Clear for cone 6.'),
